pd_0_com_0text: *The Dog seems stuck under the rock*
pd_1_com_0text: It's okay buddy, here I'll help you!
pd_1_com_1text: This will teach you, annoying mutt! *Kick*
pd_5_com_0text: Now to return to your owner, good boy!
pd_7_com_0text: You seem to be a very helpful person. Somebody truly light of heart.He calls him somebody light of heart and grants them the Light Element.
pd_8_com_0text: It would only seem fitting that I should grant you this. The Light Element.
pd_9_com_0text: Oh my, these days you rarely meet somebody so evil.
pd_10_com_0text: Your heart is truly tainted and rotten to the core. He says that this element might suit them, giving him the Dark Element.
pd_11_com_0text: In this case,  this element might suit them. I bestow upon thee, The Dark Element.
